### ============================================================
### Piedrazul - Citas App | Pruebas API para Sustentación
### URL base: http://localhost:5184
### Auth: Development mode usa headers X-Debug-* (sin Keycloak)
### ============================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5184

### ─────────────────────────────────────────
### VARIABLES DE USUARIO (cambiar según rol)
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

### Como Paciente (rol: Patient)
@subjectPaciente = demo-patient
@nombrePaciente  = Paciente Demo
@emailPaciente   = paciente.demo@piedrazul.test
@rolesPaciente   = Patient

### Como Personal Interno (roles válidos: Admin | Scheduler | Doctor)
@subjectAdmin = admin-001
@nombreAdmin  = Administrador Piedrazul
@emailAdmin   = admin@piedrazul.test
@rolesAdmin   = Admin

### IDs de datos semilla (creados automáticamente por el seeder)
@docPaciente = 1000000001
@proveedorMed = MED001
@proveedorTer = TER001
@proveedorPsi = PSI001


### ============================================================
### 1. HEALTH CHECK
### ============================================================

### 1.1 Verificar que la API está viva
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health


### ============================================================
### 2. ENDPOINTS PÚBLICOS (sin autenticación)
### ============================================================

### 2.1 Información del centro médico
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/public/info

###

### 2.2 Listar proveedores disponibles
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/public/providers

###

### 2.3 Ver disponibilidad de un proveedor por fecha
### Cambia la fecha al próximo lunes (o un día con horario configurado)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/public/providers/{{proveedorMed}}/availability?date=2026-05-11

###

### 2.4 Buscar paciente por número de documento
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/public/patients/lookup?document={{docPaciente}}

###

### 2.5 Ver citas de un paciente por documento (sin login)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/public/appointments/by-document?document={{docPaciente}}

###

### 2.6 Crear cita pública (sin login)
### *** ESTE REQUEST DISPARA EL EVENTO RABBITMQ ***
### Cambia appointmentDate y startTime a un slot disponible
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/public/appointments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "providerId": "{{proveedorMed}}",
  "patientDocument": "9999999999",
  "patientName": "Juan García",
  "patientEmail": "juan.garcia@test.com",
  "patientPhone": "3109876543",
  "appointmentDate": "2026-05-12",
  "startTime": "08:00"
}


### ============================================================
### 3. ENDPOINTS DE PACIENTE (requiere autenticación Patient)
### ============================================================

### 3.1 Ver mi perfil de paciente
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patient/profile
X-Debug-Subject: {{subjectPaciente}}
X-Debug-Name: {{nombrePaciente}}
X-Debug-Email: {{emailPaciente}}
X-Debug-Roles: {{rolesPaciente}}

###

### 3.2 Crear/actualizar mi perfil
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/patient/profile
Content-Type: application/json
X-Debug-Subject: {{subjectPaciente}}
X-Debug-Name: {{nombrePaciente}}
X-Debug-Email: {{emailPaciente}}
X-Debug-Roles: {{rolesPaciente}}

{
  "document": "{{docPaciente}}",
  "name": "Paciente Demo",
  "email": "{{emailPaciente}}",
  "phone": "3001234567",
  "gender": "Female",
  "birthDate": "1992-05-12"
}

###

### 3.3 Ver mis citas como paciente autenticado
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patient/appointments
X-Debug-Subject: {{subjectPaciente}}
X-Debug-Name: {{nombrePaciente}}
X-Debug-Email: {{emailPaciente}}
X-Debug-Roles: {{rolesPaciente}}

###

### 3.4 Crear cita como paciente autenticado
### *** ESTE REQUEST TAMBIÉN DISPARA EL EVENTO RABBITMQ ***
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/patient/appointments
Content-Type: application/json
X-Debug-Subject: {{subjectPaciente}}
X-Debug-Name: {{nombrePaciente}}
X-Debug-Email: {{emailPaciente}}
X-Debug-Roles: {{rolesPaciente}}

{
  "providerId": "{{proveedorTer}}",
  "appointmentDate": "2026-05-12",
  "startTime": "08:00"
}

###

### 3.5 Cancelar mi cita (reemplaza {id} con el ID de una cita real)
### *** ESTE REQUEST DISPARA appointment.status en RabbitMQ ***
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/patient/appointments/{id}/cancel
X-Debug-Subject: {{subjectPaciente}}
X-Debug-Name: {{nombrePaciente}}
X-Debug-Email: {{emailPaciente}}
X-Debug-Roles: {{rolesPaciente}}


### ============================================================
### 4. ENDPOINTS INTERNOS (roles: Admin | Scheduler | Doctor)
### ============================================================

### 4.1 Buscar pacientes (interno)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/internal/patients/search?q=Demo
X-Debug-Subject: {{subjectAdmin}}
X-Debug-Name: {{nombreAdmin}}
X-Debug-Email: {{emailAdmin}}
X-Debug-Roles: {{rolesAdmin}}

###

### 4.2 Ver citas por proveedor y fecha
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/internal/appointments?providerId={{proveedorMed}}&date=2026-05-12
X-Debug-Subject: {{subjectAdmin}}
X-Debug-Name: {{nombreAdmin}}
X-Debug-Email: {{emailAdmin}}
X-Debug-Roles: {{rolesAdmin}}

###

### 4.3 Crear cita interna
### *** DISPARA appointment.created en RabbitMQ ***
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/internal/appointments
Content-Type: application/json
X-Debug-Subject: {{subjectAdmin}}
X-Debug-Name: {{nombreAdmin}}
X-Debug-Email: {{emailAdmin}}
X-Debug-Roles: {{rolesAdmin}}

{
  "providerId": "{{proveedorPsi}}",
  "patientDocument": "1000000001",
  "appointmentDate": "2026-05-16",
  "startTime": "09:00",
  "notes": "Cita creada desde prueba interna"
}

###

### 4.4 Cambiar estado de una cita (reemplaza {id} con ID real)
### *** DISPARA appointment.status en RabbitMQ ***
### status válidos: Confirmed | Completed | Cancelled | NoShow
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/internal/appointments/{id}/status
Content-Type: application/json
X-Debug-Subject: {{subjectAdmin}}
X-Debug-Name: {{nombreAdmin}}
X-Debug-Email: {{emailAdmin}}
X-Debug-Roles: {{rolesAdmin}}

{
  "status": "Confirmed"
}

###

### 4.5 Reprogramar una cita (reemplaza {id} con ID real)
### *** DISPARA appointment.status en RabbitMQ ***
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/internal/appointments/{id}/reschedule
Content-Type: application/json
X-Debug-Subject: {{subjectAdmin}}
X-Debug-Name: {{nombreAdmin}}
X-Debug-Email: {{emailAdmin}}
X-Debug-Roles: {{rolesAdmin}}

{
  "appointmentDate": "2026-05-13",
  "startTime": "10:00"
}

###

### 4.6 Ver historial de una cita (reemplaza {id} con ID real)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/internal/appointments/{id}/history
X-Debug-Subject: {{subjectAdmin}}
X-Debug-Name: {{nombreAdmin}}
X-Debug-Email: {{emailAdmin}}
X-Debug-Roles: {{rolesAdmin}}

###

### 4.7 Exportar citas a PDF
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/internal/appointments/export/pdf?providerId={{proveedorMed}}&date=2026-05-12
X-Debug-Subject: {{subjectAdmin}}
X-Debug-Name: {{nombreAdmin}}
X-Debug-Email: {{emailAdmin}}
X-Debug-Roles: {{rolesAdmin}}

###

### 4.8 Exportar citas a CSV
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/internal/appointments/export/csv?providerId={{proveedorMed}}&date=2026-05-12
X-Debug-Subject: {{subjectAdmin}}
X-Debug-Name: {{nombreAdmin}}
X-Debug-Email: {{emailAdmin}}
X-Debug-Roles: {{rolesAdmin}}


### ============================================================
### 5. ENDPOINTS DE ADMINISTRACIÓN (solo rol: Admin)
### ============================================================

### 5.1 Ver configuración del sistema
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/settings
X-Debug-Subject: {{subjectAdmin}}
X-Debug-Name: {{nombreAdmin}}
X-Debug-Email: {{emailAdmin}}
X-Debug-Roles: {{rolesAdmin}}

###

### 5.2 Actualizar configuración
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/settings
Content-Type: application/json
X-Debug-Subject: {{subjectAdmin}}
X-Debug-Name: {{nombreAdmin}}
X-Debug-Email: {{emailAdmin}}
X-Debug-Roles: {{rolesAdmin}}

{
  "weeksAhead": 8,
  "timezone": "America/Bogota"
}

###

### 5.3 Ver horarios de proveedores
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/provider-schedules
X-Debug-Subject: {{subjectAdmin}}
X-Debug-Name: {{nombreAdmin}}
X-Debug-Email: {{emailAdmin}}
X-Debug-Roles: {{rolesAdmin}}

###

### 5.4 Crear horario de proveedor
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/provider-schedules
Content-Type: application/json
X-Debug-Subject: {{subjectAdmin}}
X-Debug-Name: {{nombreAdmin}}
X-Debug-Email: {{emailAdmin}}
X-Debug-Roles: {{rolesAdmin}}

{
  "providerId": "{{proveedorMed}}",
  "dayOfWeek": "Monday",
  "startTime": "08:00",
  "endTime": "12:00",
  "slotDurationMinutes": 30
}

###

### 5.5 Buscar pacientes (admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/patients?q=Demo
X-Debug-Subject: {{subjectAdmin}}
X-Debug-Name: {{nombreAdmin}}
X-Debug-Email: {{emailAdmin}}
X-Debug-Roles: {{rolesAdmin}}
